Package: BioThermR
Type: Package
Title: Standardized Processing and Analysis of Thermal Imaging Data in Animal Studies
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "BeiHao", "Li",
      email = "szright2000@gmail.com",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: A comprehensive framework for the standardized analysis of thermal
    imaging data in animal experimentation. It integrates data import
    (FLIR, raw, CSV), automated and interactive Region of Interest (ROI)
    segmentation, and high-throughput batch processing.
